# Netlify / hosts that honor _redirects.
# Do NOT add `/* /index.html 200` here — Cloudflare Workers SPA
# (assets.not_found_handling) already does that, and the catch-all
# causes deploy error 100324 (infinite redirect loop).
#
# Static OAuth bounce so Safari returns to the app without the SPA.
/native-sso-callback /native-sso-callback/index.html 200
/native-sso-callback/ /native-sso-callback/index.html 200
